  "description": "11e GDM card-action player prompt (multi-pick): P2 plays Smoke and Mirrors (Disruption vs Reconnaissance). The P1 centre garrison withdraws and Warboss B takes obj_center, so P2 controls two non-home objectives. End Turn opens the CardActionDialog with both Decoy checkboxes pre-selected (mirroring the auto-resolve); the player unchecks obj_nml_2 (where P1's Shield Captain would scrub the marker anyway) and confirms — only obj_center is Decoyed (2 VP + 2 enemy-territory bonus for the central objective = 4 VP). decoyed_ever staying at exactly one entry proves the auto-pick stood down for the unchosen objective; the turn then ends.",
  "steps": [
